        <tr><td>Main control board</td><td>$380 – $580</td><td>Electronic generations</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor start / run capacitor</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>8–12 year service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor replacement (post-warranty)</td><td>$900 – $1,500</td><td>Rare root cause</td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Broader reference: <a href="/price-list/refrigerator-repair-cost/">refrigerator repair cost
        guide</a>. Sibling brands: <a href="/brands/kitchenaid-refrigerator-repair/">KitchenAid</a>,
        <a href="/brands/maytag-refrigerator-repair/">Maytag</a>,
        <a href="/brands/amana-refrigerator-repair/">Amana</a>,
        <a href="/brands/jennair-refrigerator-repair/">JennAir</a>,
        <a href="/brands/roper-refrigerator-repair/">Roper</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Service areas, where our Whirlpool calls come from</h2>
      <div class="area-grid">
